snippet.title: [Mandrake Girls ~Garden of Secret~] Promotion video
snippet.description:
Precious little mandrake-girls are just waiting for you to discover them!
Just plant your seeds and wait for them to sprout.
Upgrade your flower pots to find rare mandrakes with adorable stories!
Plus, find gorgeous artwork to add to your collection.
We welcome you to Garden of Secret.
